              name: "Discuss Online",
              sidebar:
                "---\n\n# Welcome\n\nA community for anything and everything that's not terrible.\n\nLet's talk! But not like in a \"your partner saw you looking up bunnies with pancakes on their heads\" talk. Let's talk about anything and everything. Like how much we love bunnies with pancakes on their heads!\n\nIf you have questions about [Lemmy](https://join-lemmy.org/) or how the [fediverse](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fediverse) works, checkout [this post](https://discuss.online/post/646).\n\n## Sister sites\n- [Utter.Online (Mastodon)](https://utter.online/) - Open Registration\n- [Social.Photo (Pixelfed)](https://social.photo/) - Open Registration\n\n## Donations... if you can spare it\n- [Github Sponsors](https://github.com/sponsors/jgrim)\n- [Patreon](https://patreon.com/discussonline)\n- [OpenCollective](https://opencollective.com/discussonline/donate/)\n\n[![GitHub Sponsors](https://img.shields.io/github/sponsors/jgrim?style=for-the-badge)](https://github.com/sponsors/jgrim)\n![https://opencollective.com/discussonline/](https://opencollective.com/discussonline/tiers/badge.svg)\n\n---\n\n\n## Rules\n\n1. No bigotry - including racism, sexism, ableism, homophobia, transphobia, or xenophobia. Code of Conduct.\n2. Be respectful. Everyone should feel welcome here.\n3. No porn\n4. No Ads / Spamming.\n5. Follow the [Lemmy Code of Conduct](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/code_of_conduct.html)\n\n---\n\n## Links\n- [Mastodon: @discussonline@utter.online](https://utter.online/@discussonline)\n- [!new_here](https://discuss.online/c/new_here)\n- [Matrix: #online.discuss:discuss.online](https://matrix.to/#/#online.discuss:discuss.online)\n- [Matrix: #community-channels:discuss.online](https://matrix.to/#/#community-channels:discuss.online)\n- [Server Status](https://status.discuss.online/)\n- [Wiki](https://wiki.discuss.online/)\n\n---\n\n## Matrix\nThe matrix server is live with public rooms. Registration is open. Get your free @[you]@discuss.online username. [element.discuss.online](https://element.discuss.online/)\n\n---\n\n## Mastodon\nI have created a Mastodon server. Registration is open. Get your @[you]@utter.online username. [utter.online](https://utter.online/)\n\n---\n\n## Contact the admin\n- Matrix\n  - [@jgrim:discuss.online](http://matrix.to/#/@jgrim:discuss.online)\n- Mastodon\n  - [@jsonarray@utter.online](https://utter.online/@jsonarray)\n- Email\n  - [hello@discuss.online](mailto:hello@discuss.online)\n\n---\n## Metrics\n![](https://lemmy-status.org/api/v1/endpoints/_discuss-online/health/badge.svg)\n\n![](https://lemmy-status.org/api/v1/endpoints/_discuss-online/uptimes/7d/badge.svg)\n\n![](https://lemmy-status.org/api/v1/endpoints/_discuss-online/uptimes/24h/badge.svg)\n\n![](https://lemmy-status.org/api/v1/endpoints/_discuss-online/uptimes/1h/badge.svg)\n\n---\n\n\n[![](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/endorsements/discuss.online.svg)](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/endorsements/discuss.online)\n[![](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/guarantees/discuss.online.svg)](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/whitelist/discuss.online)\n\n---\n\n***The statistics below reflect the usage of local users.** Users can interact with any instance in the fediverse. Creating posts and comments count towards interactions. You may see a lot more activity than listed below generated from external users.*",
